{"items":[{"id":"998352","user":{"id":"7900903","nickname":"沐夏_IMuXia","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfNzkwMDkwM183OTAwOTAzXzE2NTY1NzcwMTY3ODFfYjA2NTI4Y2Y.jpeg","subject_id":8623,"work_shop_name":"简单·编程","work_shop_level":1,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p>&nbsp;</p> \n<p>从等式的一边移项到另一边，正号变负号，负号变正号。</p> \n<p>把方程两边都加上（或减去）同一个数或同一个整式，就相当于把方程中的某些项改变符号后，从方程的一边移到另一边，这样的变形叫做移项。</p> \n<p>如：x+1=2，把等式左边的1移到右边，就是x=2+（-1）。或者x=2-1。</p> \n<p>如：x-1=2，把等式左边的1移到右边，就是x=2+（+1）。或者x=2+1。</p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1621680225,"created_at":1621680225,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76395","user":{"id":"449719","nickname":"急躁的萌萌熊685","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/8236cff0-077f-484a-9be6-58777bc64559","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p>谢谢</p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1524225807,"created_at":1524225807,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76359","user":{"id":"148022","nickname":"I桔汁糖浆I","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTQ4MDIyXzE0ODAyMl8xNjA1MTkwODQwMTg5XzU2NDVmYWY2.png","subject_id":615,"work_shop_name":"萌新院","work_shop_level":2,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>方程两边同时加、减、乘、除相同的数时，方程仍然成立。</p>\n<p>举个例子，假设这里有个方程：</p>\n<p>4x+8=12</p>\n<p>我们可以在两边同时减去8：</p>\n<p>4x+8-8=12-8，可得到4x=4</p>\n<p>此时两边通除以4，得：</p>\n<p>4x/4=4/4，可得到x=1</p>\n<p>知道这个后，我们用这个方程来举例：4-x=2</p>\n<p>我们先在两边同时加上x：</p>\n<p>4-x+x=2+x，可得到4=2+x</p>\n<p>此时你可以发现x前面的符号从减号变成加号了，这样就可以像上面的方法那样解出这个方程。这就是我们所说的变号。通俗易懂的来讲，当方程某边的某个数移动到另一边时，符号就会发生变化，加减号互变，乘除号互变。</p>\n<p>至于变出了除号，这时候不能用乘法分配律，如果没有学到初中的倒数的话，应该就做不下去了，所以还是不推荐在方程含有加减号的时候把乘号移到另一边去变成除号。</p>\n<p>在初中你会学到负数，把方程两边同乘以一个负数时，方程的整体都会变号。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1524146375,"created_at":1524146375,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"76356","user":{"id":"297000","nickname":"幻_想","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fnz8yiIuB9eiZvR-SV4kwt1q3hi0","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>移项？</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1524142570,"created_at":1524142570,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":4,"counted":true}